    "composer": "Chico Cesar",
    "lyricsHtml": "\n    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Gm7\">Gm7</span>           <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Eb\">Eb</span>       <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Cm7\">Cm7</span>     <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Cm7\">Cm7</span> <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Cm/Bb\">Cm/Bb</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Respeitem meus cabelos, brancos</span>\n   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am5-/7\">Am5-/7</span>          <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D7/F#\">D7/F#</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Chegou a hora de falar</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D7/9\">D7/9</span>          <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Gm7\">Gm7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Vamos ser francos</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Gm7\">Gm7</span>                   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#º\">F#º</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Pois quando um preto fala</span>\n                           <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F7\">F7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">O branco cala ou deixa a sala</span>\n       <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Bb\">Bb</span>           <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Bb\">Bb</span>   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F/A\">F/A</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Com veludo nos tamancos</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Gm7\">Gm7</span>           <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am5-/7\">Am5-/7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Cabelo veio da África</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D7/9\">D7/9</span>              <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Gm7\">Gm7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Junto com meus santos.(Bis)</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Gm7\">Gm7</span>          <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#º\">F#º</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Benguelas, zulus, gêges</span>\n   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F\">F</span>              <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Bb\">Bb</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Rebolos, bundos, bantos</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Eb\">Eb</span>         <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am5-/7\">Am5-/7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Batuques, toques, mandingas</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D7/9\">D7/9</span>               <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Gm7\">Gm7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Danças, tranças, cantos</span>\n   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am5-/7\">Am5-/7</span>      <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D7/9\">D7/9</span> <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#7\">F#7</span>      <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Gm7\">Gm7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Respeitem meus cabelos, brancos</span>\n   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am5-/7\">Am5-/7</span>      <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D7/9\">D7/9</span> <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#7\">F#7</span>      <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Gm7\">Gm7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Respeitem meus cabelos, brancos</span>\n               <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Cm7\">Cm7</span>      <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Gm7\">Gm7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Se eu quero pixaim, deixa</span>\n                <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Cm7\">Cm7</span>     <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Gm7\">Gm7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Se eu quero enrolar, deixa</span>\n                <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Cm7\">Cm7</span>     <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Gm7\">Gm7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Se eu quero colorir, deixa</span>\n                <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Cm7\">Cm7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Se eu quero assanhar,</span>\n        <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Bb\">Bb</span> <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am5-/7\">Am5-/7</span> <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Eb7\">Eb7</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D7/9\">D7/9</span>   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Gm7\">Gm7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Deixa, deixa a madeixa balançar. (Bis)</span>\n\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">   Repete a musica toda.</span>\n            <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Gm7\">Gm7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">...     fui claro.</span>\n",
